2006-01-22  Christian Aistleitner  <christian.aistleitner@gmx.at>

	* updated to use LibModel 0.1.2

2005-12-05  Christian Aistleitner  <christian.aistleitner@gmx.at>

	* lib/src/framework/tst_tctl.as: added classification for unequal expression tree leaves when comparing expression trees. Fixed output of the path to the failed node for unequal expression trees in assertEqual for expression Trees.

2005-12-03  Christian Aistleitner  <christian.aistleitner@gmx.at>

	* lib/src/framework/tst_tctl.as: added output of where and why assertEquals fails for ExpressionTrees

